Simultaneous use of paved RWY and adjacent grass RWY prohibited.

properties.name: CHAMPAGNOLE CROTENAY
properties.remarks:
AD with special characteristics reserved for :
- home-based pilots.
- pilots holding a mountain rating.
- pilots with more than 250 hours of flight time who requested prior permission from the AD operator and who have recognized the platform with an instructor entitled by the AD operator. The permission  ill be maintained during 1 year and renewed under conditions by the AD operator.
- helicopters.

properties.remarks:
AD reserved for radio-equipped ACFT.
Simultaneous TKOF and/or LDG on the RWY are prohibited. All simultaneous TKOF and/or LDG on the concrete RWY must be stopped if a glider is immobilized on the half width of the grass strip
Unpaved RWY reserved for gliders and tugs ACFT

properties.name: OYONNAX ARBENT
properties.remarks:
AD reserved for radio-equipped ACFT.
No powered ACFT must enter final approach of the two AD circuits if a glider is already on final.
Very noise-sensitive AD.

properties.name: PUIVERT
properties.remarks:
AD reserved for gliders and tugs, as well as planes and ULM authorized by AD operator.
During glider winching operations and throughout their duration, radio silence is mandatory.

properties.remarks:
